stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> assigned: assign_task 動作寫入
  assigned --> in_progress: Bot 開始執行任務
  assigned --> cancelled: 取消指派
  in_progress --> done: report_task status=done
  in_progress --> blocked: 遇到阻礙
  in_progress --> cancelled: 取消執行
  blocked --> in_progress: 阻礙解除繼續
  done --> [*]: 任務完成記錄 task_events
  cancelled --> [*]: 任務取消記錄 task_events

  note right of assigned
    IntentEngine 寫入
    DB tasks 資料表
  end note
  note right of done
    DB 記錄 task_events
    狀態不可逆
  end note
